          </h2>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-secondary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-500 p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl shadow-md" id="founder-quote">
            <p class="text-lg text-dark-700 italic mb-3">
