              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Valores -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white" id="values-section">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12" id="values-header">
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-dark-900 mb-4">
            Lo que nos mueve
          </h2>
          <p class="text-dark-600 text-lg">
            M√°s que vender manga, queremos crear experiencias memorables
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6" id="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-primary-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark-900 mb-2">Pasi√≥n</h3>
                <p class="text-dark-700">
                  Somos fans como t√∫. Cada recomendaci√≥n viene del coraz√≥n, no de un algoritmo.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-secondary-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark-900 mb-2">Comunidad</h3>
                <p class="text-dark-700">
                  No eres un n√∫mero de pedido. Eres parte de una familia que comparte tu pasi√≥n.
                </p>
