            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-primary-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark-900 mb-2">Honestidad</h3>
                <p class="text-dark-700">
                  Si algo no vale la pena, te lo diremos. Preferimos tu confianza a una venta r√°pida.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-secondary-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark-900 mb-2">Dedicaci√≥n</h3>
